                         Encoder/Ripper: SMiLE                         
                                                                        
   There are a few reasons for the READNFO, the main part being that    
   the film is intended to be shown in black and white, not too         
   sure why, but just letting you know. Another saying a big thanks     
   to SiC for the nice quality release. I wasn't going to encode        
   this, as it isn't our cup of tea, but there have been hardly no      
   encodes out since SiC released theirs. I have watched this and       
   yes the movie itself is pretty horrific, it's not even that          
   shocking, it's just disturbing, i shall not be watching it again.    
   There is a warning at the start of the video, i suggest you heed     
   the warning, this is not for people that don't like torture/gore     
   or are easily offended. It's up to you if you choose to watch it     
   or not, so don't get moaning. Anyway, we dropped the file in for     
   conversion, added some of our own filters and then ran out custom    
   encode settings on it, before muxing and converting the audio.       
   Turned out nice, can be blocky sometimes but that was the same on    
   SiC's version. Don't moan and as always - Enjoy!
